INSERT INTO `zh_article` VALUES ('47', '20180520/61a404b1b5c84f8f072567d604dbf0a1.jpg', '0', '0', '1', '2', '如何使用Glyphicons', '<div class=\"bs-docs-section\" style=\"margin-bottom: 60px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;\"><h2 id=\"glyphicons-how-to-use\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">如何使用</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2em; line-height: 1.75;\">出于性能的考虑，所有图标都需要一个基类和对应每个图标的类。把下面的代码放在任何地方都可以正常使用。注意，为了设置正确的内补（padding），务必在图标和文本之间添加一个空格。</p><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-danger\" id=\"callout-glyphicons-dont-mix\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(206, 72, 68); border-image: initial; border-radius: 3px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: inherit; color: rgb(206, 72, 68); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">不要和其他组件混合使用</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75;\">图标类不能和其它组件直接联合使用。它们不能在同一个元素上与其他类共同存在。应该创建一个嵌套的&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px;\">&lt;span&gt;</code>&nbsp;标签，并将图标类应用到这个&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&lt;span&gt;</code>&nbsp;标签上。</p></div><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-danger\" id=\"callout-glyphicons-empty-only\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: -5px 0px 20px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(206, 72, 68); border-image: initial; border-radius: 3px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: inherit; color: rgb(206, 72, 68); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">只对内容为空的元素起作用</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75;\">图标类只能应用在不包含任何文本内容或子元素的元素上。</p></div><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-info\" id=\"callout-glyphicons-location\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: -5px 0px 20px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(27, 128, 158); border-image: initial; border-radius: 3px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: inherit; color: rgb(27, 128, 158); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">改变图标字体文件的位置</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2em; line-height: 1.75;\">Bootstrap 假定所有的图标字体文件全部位于&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">../fonts/</code>&nbsp;目录内，相对于预编译版 CSS 文件的目录。如果你修改了图标字体文件的位置，那么，你需要通过下面列出的任何一种方式来更新 CSS 文件：</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2em; line-height: 1.75;\"><li>在 Less 源码文件中修改&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px;\">@icon-font-path</code>&nbsp;和/或&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">@icon-font-name</code>&nbsp;变量。</li><li>利用 Less 编译器提供的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://lesscss.org/usage/#command-line-usage-relative-urls\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">相对 URL 地址选项</a>。</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">修改预编译 CSS 文件中的&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">url()</code>&nbsp;地址。</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75;\">根据你自身的情况选择一种方式即可。</p></div><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-warning\" id=\"callout-glyphicons-accessibility\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: -5px 0px 20px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(170, 103, 8); border-image: initial; border-radius: 3px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: inherit; color: rgb(170, 103, 8); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">图标的可访问性</h4><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2em; line-height: 1.75;\">现代的辅助技术能够识别并朗读由 CSS 生成的内容和特定的 Unicode 字符。为了避免 屏幕识读设备抓取非故意的和可能产生混淆的输出内容（尤其是当图标纯粹作为装饰用途时），我们为这些图标设置了&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">aria-hidden=\"true\"</code>&nbsp;属性。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2em; line-height: 1.75;\">如果你使用图标是为了表达某些含义（不仅仅是为了装饰用），请确保你所要表达的意思能够通过被辅助设备识别，例如，包含额外的内容并通过&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">.sr-only</code>&nbsp;类让其在视觉上表现出隐藏的效果。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75;\">如果你所创建的组件不包含任何文本内容（例如，&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px;\">&lt;button&gt;</code>&nbsp;内只包含了一个图标），你应当提供其他的内容来表示这个控件的意图，这样就能让使用辅助设备的用户知道其作用了。这种情况下，你可以为控件添加&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">aria-label</code>&nbsp;属性。</p></div><figure class=\"highlight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 9px 14px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 232); border-radius: 4px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: normal; background-color: transparent; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; white-space: nowrap;\"><code class=\"language-html\" data-lang=\"html\" style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; padding-right: 45px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block;\"><span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: rgb(47, 111, 159);\">&lt;span</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 159, 207);\">class=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 73, 80);\">\"glyphicon glyphicon-search\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 159, 207);\">aria-hidden=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 73, 80);\">\"true\"</span><span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: rgb(47, 111, 159);\">&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</span></code></pre></figure><h2 id=\"glyphicons-examples\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a class=\"anchorjs-link \" href=\"https://v3.bootcss.com/components/#glyphicons-examples\" aria-label=\"Anchor link for: glyphicons examples\" data-anchorjs-icon=\"\" style=\"color: inherit; opacity: 0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: anchorjs-icons; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: inherit; position: absolute; margin-left: -1em; padding-right: 0.5em;\"></a>实例</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2em; line-height: 1.75;\">可以把它们应用到按钮、工具条中的按钮组、导航或输入框等地方。</p><div class=\"bs-example\" data-example-id=\"glyphicons-general\" style=\"position: relative; padding: 45px 15px 15px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; box-shadow: none; border-radius: 4px 4px 0px 0px;\"><div class=\"btn-toolbar\" role=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"btn-group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default\" aria-label=\"Left Align\" style=\"line-height: 1.42857;\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-align-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default\" aria-label=\"Center Align\" style=\"line-height: 1.42857;\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-align-center\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default\" aria-label=\"Right Align\" style=\"line-height: 1.42857;\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-align-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default\" aria-label=\"Justify\" style=\"line-height: 1.42857;\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-align-justify\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button></div></div><div class=\"btn-toolbar\" role=\"toolbar\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default btn-lg\" style=\"line-height: 1.33333;\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>&nbsp;Star</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default\" style=\"line-height: 1.42857;\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>&nbsp;Star</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default btn-sm\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>&nbsp;Star</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-default btn-xs\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>&nbsp;Star</button></div></div><figure class=\"highlight\" style=\"margin-top: -16px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 9px 14px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); border: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 232); border-radius: 0px 0px 4px 4px;\"><pre style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: normal; background-color: transparent; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; white-space: nowrap;\"><code class=\"language-html\" data-lang=\"html\" style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; padding-right: 45px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block;\"><span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: rgb(47, 111, 159);\">&lt;button</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 159, 207);\">type=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 73, 80);\">\"button\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 159, 207);\">class=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 73, 80);\">\"btn btn-default\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 159, 207);\">aria-label=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 73, 80);\">\"Left Align\"</span